## Resources Especiales

### AuthResource (Usuario + Token)

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Http\Resources;

class AuthResource extends ApiResource
{
    public function toArray($request): array
    {
        return [
            'id' => $this->id,
            'name' => $this->name,
            'email' => $this->email,
            'token' => $this->token ?? null,  // Token agregado dinámicamente
        ];
    }
}
```

### DashboardResource (Datos Agregados)

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Http\Resources;

class DashboardResource extends ApiResource
{
    public function toArray($request): array
    {
        // $this->resource es un array, no un modelo
        return [
            'total_users' => $this->resource['total_users'],
            'total_orders' => $this->resource['total_orders'],
            'revenue_today' => number_format($this->resource['revenue_today'], 2),
            'generated_at' => now()->toIso8601String(),
        ];
    }
}
```

Uso en controlador:

```php
$metrics = $this->dashboardService->getMetrics();
return $this->successResponse(new DashboardResource($metrics));
```

