## Collections

### Estructura Base

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Http\Resources;

class ProductCollection extends ApiCollection
{
    // Hereda paginación automática de ApiCollection
}
```

### Formato de Respuesta Automático

`ApiCollection` genera:

```json
{
  "data": [...],
  "meta": {
    "pagination": {
      "total": 100,
      "count": 10,
      "per_page": 10,
      "current_page": 1,
      "total_pages": 10,
      "has_more_pages": true
    }
  }
}
```

### Collection Personalizada

Para agregar metadatos adicionales:

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Http\Resources;

class ProductCollection extends ApiCollection
{
    public function toArray($request): array
    {
        $result = parent::toArray($request);
        
        $result['meta']['filters'] = [
            'available_statuses' => ['active', 'inactive'],
            'price_range' => [
                'min' => $this->collection->min('price'),
                'max' => $this->collection->max('price'),
            ],
        ];
        
        return $result;
    }
}
```

